        <Parent_String>double-enders [300232704], symmetrical-ended watercraft [300232703], watercraft by end configuration [300232685], watercraft by form [300232663], watercraft by specific type [300219289], watercraft [300042940], vehicles (transportation) [300219258], Transportation Vehicles (hierarchy name) [300042929], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
